Awkwafina (Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings, The Farewell, Crazy Rich Asians) is the creator and writer of the hit comedy series inspired by her real-life growing up in Queens, NY. Raised by her Dad (BD Wong) and Grandma (Lori Tan Chinn) alongside her cousin (Bowen Yang), Nora Lin leans on her family as she navigates life and young adulthood in outer borough-NYC.Season 2 of Awkwafina is Nora From Queens will premiere on Saturday Night Origi-Lols - an unfiltered, unapologetic, and undeniably hilarious Saturday night segment that will keep comedy lovers entertained with brand new Comedy Central original content that has never been seen on the continent before.Be sure to tune into Awkwafina is Nora From Queens on Saturday 28 August at 22:30 CAT (on Comedy Central Africa DStv Channel 122)For more on Comedy Central (DStv channel 122), follow @comedycentralaf (Twitter and Instagram) and Comedy Central Africa on Facebook. For more visit our website: www.comedycentralafrica.com.